					<description><![CDATA[This is my .screenrc: startup_message off vbell off split screen -t s1 1 ssh s1 split -v focus down screen -t s2 2 ssh s2 focus down screen -t s3 3 ssh s3 split -v focus down screen -t s4 4 ssh s4 focus top And you can see the screen shot at right. This <a href='https://xiehang.com/blog/2010/03/05/screenrc/' class='excerpt-more'>[...]</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen.jpg"></a><a href="https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-954" title="screen" src="https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen-300x185.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="185" srcset="https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen-300x185.jpg 300w, https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen-1024x633.jpg 1024w, https://xiehang.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/03/screen.jpg 1082w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></a>This is my .screenrc:</p>
<blockquote><p>startup_message off<br />
vbell off<br />
split<br />
screen -t s1 1 ssh s1<br />
split -v<br />
focus down<br />
screen -t s2 2 ssh s2<br />
focus down<br />
screen -t s3 3 ssh s3<br />
split -v<br />
focus down<br />
screen -t s4 4 ssh s4<br />
focus top</p></blockquote>
<p>And you can see the screen shot at right.</p>
